title: Rare Hits of The 80s Vol. 67
description:
For your listening pleasure and to introduce a few more obscure 80 bands to a wider audience, guys and gals, here's Rare Hits of The 80's Vol. 67. This installment features some very interesting bands and a variety of style ,  synthwave minimal tracks from, Future State, King Rockit , The Impolight, and Silent Creatures, Tranquil Eyes, pure new wave tracks in  Darius And The Magnets, Via Marconi,  Alastair Riddell, Boys Say Go and  Volumatix as well as some new wave alternative songs by Systems Of Romance,  Tame & Talking,  Shadowboys and  Lung Overcoat. Please seed and enjoy. I am interested to know if there was a particular band that you liked that was new to you.
